---
import AboutHeroImage from '../assets/blog-placeholder-about.jpg';
import Layout from '../layouts/BlogPost.astro';
---

<Layout
	title="About Me"
	description="Principal Software Engineer with expertise in embedded systems, digital TV middleware, and full-stack development"
	pubDate={new Date('August 08 2021')}
	heroImage={AboutHeroImage}
>
	<h2>Professional Experience</h2>

	<div class="experience-section">
		<h3>Principal Software Engineer</h3>
		<div class="company-info">
			<strong>Sky</strong> · Full-time
			<span class="duration">Sep 2014 - Present · 11 yrs 2 mos</span>
			<span class="location">London Area, United Kingdom · Hybrid</span>
		</div>
		<p>
			Integrated external applications into Sky Platforms such as BBC iPlayer, Prime Video, HaYu, and others, 
			liaising with internal and external teams across multiple departments including QA, Program and Project 
			Managers, Product and Engineering. Created and delivered embedded JavaScript libraries namely RDK Firebolt 
			and authored Python tools to orchestrate application delivery. Investigated incidents and triaged problems 
			organizing and providing options to solutions in different domains used by Sky products.
		</p>
		<p>
			Delivered embedded telemetry and debugging tools and triaged issues carrying out detailed investigations 
			and analysis to support development teams, creating solutions in multiple domains such as DRM, UI, 
			Middleware, Players, and Web Apps for several Sky Glass, Sky Stream, and Sky Q across territories.
		</p>
		<p>
			Orchestrated the firmware delivery for Sky Set-up boxes, developing and maintaining the full stack build 
			system, integrating drivers, middleware, and the UI using internal and build pipelines. Built tools and 
			systems to automate and test the deliveries, including advanced device farm operation and log parsing 
			capabilities with automatic fault detection.
		</p>
	</div>

	<div class="experience-section">
		<h3>Software Engineer</h3>
		<div class="company-info">
			<strong>LG Electronics</strong> · Full-time
			<span class="duration">Sep 2010 - Sep 2014 · 4 yrs 1 mo</span>
			<span class="location">Greater São Paulo Area · On-site</span>
		</div>
		<p>
			Developed and maintained digital television middleware using Embedded C / C++, including Linux and 
			associated tools. ATSC and DVB Test and Live Stream validation for software integration of modules 
			and components in the NetCast and WebOS software stacks.
		</p>
		<p>
			Collaborated with QA and development teams to address field and factory issues through firmware updates 
			and process improvements.
		</p>
		<p>
			Implemented Brazil's DTV specification on various platforms, spending over a year with teams in South 
			Korea for software integration and device firmware development. Responsibilities included platform 
			bring-up work such as eMMC partitioning, Linux kernel configuration, and graphics/UI setup.
		</p>
		<p>
			Provided support for the integration of Smart TV applications, including guidance on SDK usage, code 
			snippets, and sample applications for local and global partners.
		</p>
		<div class="key-projects">
			<h4>Key Projects:</h4>
			<ul>
				<li>Developer for ISDB-T SI</li>
				<li>Developer for Ginga middleware (Brazilian DTV Interactive Applications)</li>
				<li>Porting middleware for LG DTVs spanning from 2011 to 2015</li>
				<li>Support for local applications and content partners for 2011 Smart TV</li>
				<li>Satellite prototype development for Brazil-based Europe 2011 Smart TV</li>
				<li>Implementation of Audio Deficient (AD) Brazil's specification on 2012 models</li>
			</ul>
		</div>
	</div>

	<div class="experience-section">
		<h3>Software Engineer</h3>
		<div class="company-info">
			<strong>Gertec</strong> · Full-time
			<span class="duration">Sep 2007 - Sep 2010 · 3 yrs 1 mo</span>
			<span class="location">Greater São Paulo Area · On-site</span>
		</div>
		<p>
			Delivered firmware for commercial automation products such as Price Scanners, Security Tokens and Media 
			Displays using C / C++ with Embedded Linux, RTOS, and Bare Metal including driver and display 
			configuration, barcode library integration and porting code for newer chips based on ARM and MIPS. 
			Contributed to the development of testing tools and supporting libraries.
		</p>
		<p>
			Developed banking security devices such as Card Reader, POS Systems and Secure ATM Keyboards for banking 
			and payment systems, specializing in the provisioning of keys in high-security systems. Facilitated the 
			implementation of cryptography functions and designed APIs for device control and communication for 
			Windows and Linux.
		</p>
		<div class="key-projects">
			<h4>Key Projects:</h4>
			<ul>
				<li>ATM cryptographic keyboard</li>
				<li>Pin Pad and POS devices</li>
				<li>Multimedia solution for Display ADs</li>
				<li>Price checking systems</li>
				<li>Token devices</li>
			</ul>
		</div>
	</div>

	<h2>Education</h2>
	<div class="education-section">
		<h3>Bachelor's degree, Electrical and Computer Engineering</h3>
		<div class="company-info">
			<strong>FEI</strong>
			<span class="duration">Jan 2004 - Dec 2008</span>
		</div>
	</div>

	<h2>Volunteering</h2>
	<div class="volunteering-section">
		<h3>Mentor</h3>
		<div class="company-info">
			<strong>Soul Bilíngue</strong>
			<span class="duration">Dec 2022 - Present · 2 yrs 11 mos</span>
		</div>
	</div>
</Layout>

<style>
	.experience-section,
	.education-section,
	.volunteering-section {
		margin: 2rem 0;
		padding: 1.5rem;
		border-left: 4px solid var(--accent);
		background: rgba(var(--accent-rgb, 0, 102, 179), 0.05);
		border-radius: 0 8px 8px 0;
	}

	.experience-section h3,
	.education-section h3,
	.volunteering-section h3 {
		margin: 0 0 0.5rem 0;
		color: var(--accent);
		font-size: 1.3rem;
	}

	.company-info {
		margin-bottom: 1rem;
		font-size: 0.95rem;
		color: var(--text-muted, #666);
	}

	.company-info strong {
		color: var(--text);
		font-weight: 600;
	}

	.duration,
	.location {
		display: block;
		margin-top: 0.25rem;
		font-size: 0.9rem;
	}

	.key-projects {
		margin-top: 1.5rem;
		padding: 1rem;
		background: rgba(var(--accent-rgb, 0, 102, 179), 0.1);
		border-radius: 6px;
	}

	.key-projects h4 {
		margin: 0 0 0.75rem 0;
		color: var(--accent);
		font-size: 1.1rem;
	}

	.key-projects ul {
		margin: 0;
		padding-left: 1.5rem;
	}

	.key-projects li {
		margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
		color: var(--text);
	}

	.experience-section p {
		margin-bottom: 1rem;
		line-height: 1.6;
		color: var(--text);
	}

	.experience-section p:last-child {
		margin-bottom: 0;
	}

	@media (max-width: 768px) {
		.experience-section,
		.education-section,
		.volunteering-section {
			padding: 1rem;
			margin: 1.5rem 0;
		}
	}
</style>
